title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Jul 16 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Jul 16 2021
description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 1: L.A. County reinstitutes a mask mandate, even for those fully vaccinated. How long until other liberal cities follow suit? Six vaccinated New York Yankees tested positive for covid, canceling the Red Sox matchup. We are at the phase where mask non-compliance has to happen. Buck: Admit this mask stuff is total crap, absolute malarkey. Who are the moms who will lead this yoga-clad revolution? Why is nobody talking about natural immunity? Callers give their support to the mask revolution.
